OL,3,GNorthern Ireland
OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FA little light rain possible in
OL,6,Fthe north and west at first. Otherwise
OL,7,Fmainly dry and cloudy with a few
OL,8,Fbright or sunny intervals breaking
OL,9,Fthrough in the south.
OL,10,
OL,11,CTonight:FIt will be a dry and mostly
OL,12,Fcloudy evening with some late sunny
OL,13,Fintervals in the south. Remaining dry
OL,14,Fand mostly cloudy overnight.
OL,15,
OL,16,CWednesday:FA dry day and mostly cloudy
OL,17,Fin the north and west but the south
OL,18,Fand east seeing some good sunny spells
OL,19,Fbreaking through. Warm in the sunshine.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
